'''Kelada starport''' was a [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Kelada/Legends|Kelada]]. It was comprised of a myriad of warehouses and [[Hangar/Legends|docking bays]], and was the location of [[Lorana's Labyrinth]].

